('kab', 0, 'kabyle', 'Kabyle', 'taqbaylit', 'Ye nnad izirthi, ne tsakey kan ayen swayes in wulef. Imdhanen ur san ara y wekth i thmusni. Tsarend kan ayen i hgan siheraren. Sgwaken n qethwan iheraren i znuzen thadukli, imdhanen ur san ara imdukwal. Ma the vgher amdakwel, alesiyé.<br>Ye nnad izirthi qim dhi le hna. Atsan serya inu, dhan i sehyen. Tha mughli nel kayen tseqed sgul. Ey ni lan dhe ssah its wafer af allen<br>', '', '', 'khlifa ouidr houidir@hotmail.com de la région de Beni-Douala, Tizi Ouzou :', 1, 25, 'Kabylie', 36.817, 4.3),
